                	<h3>Whale Watching Tour In Mirissa Day Tour</h3>
                    <h5> Mirissa Whale Watching Tour from Ahungalla | whale watching tours In SL | Mirissa Whale Watching Tours </h5><br>
                    <p class="day-tour_para">Whale and dolphin watching in Mirissa is one of the most exciting water activities you can do in Sri Lanka during your holiday. Mirissa is the best place to start your whale and dolphin watching tour in Sri Lanka. In the warm Indian Ocean, you can see various species of whales including Blue whales, Bryde´s whales, Sperm whales, Fin whales, even sometimes Killer whales. Not only that, you can keep on the lookout for some common dolphins, Bottlenose dolphins, Spinner dolphins, Risso's dolphins, and Striped dolphins. Sometimes you can even see turtles and various fish species, for example, Bluefin tuna and flying fish, so this tour is perfect if you love all things sea.
</p>
                    <div class="container">
                        <p style="color:#168EEA; font-size:large;"><b>Do this because</b></p>
                        <ul>
                            	<li>Learn amazing facts about the largest whales and the friendly dolphins</li>
                                <li>See different kinds of Blue whales, Bryde's whales, Sperm whales, Fin whales, and sometimes Killer whales</li>
                                <li>Witness Bottlenose dolphins, Spinner dolphins, Risso's dolphins, and Striped dolphins in their natural space</li>
                                
                               
                                
                            </ul>
                    </div>
